      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Slice the <strong>cucumber </strong>into rounds</p><p>Wash the <strong>gem lettuce</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Once everything's almost ready, add the <strong>shredded gem lettuce</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>cucumber rounds</strong> to the bowl of dressing and give everything a gentle mix</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
